data.title: Reutlingen Germany
data.meta_description: Reutlingen Germany - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This fact sheet provides information about study programs in Operations Management at ESB Business School of Reutlingen University in Germany. It outlines general information about contact details and programs. It also details study information such as course loads, languages, and term dates. The application process and required documents are described. Finally, information is given about facilities and accommodation, including housing costs and living expenses.
